{"tid":2021952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒指台積電停止接受華為新訂單 市場憂慮華為出貨量 舜宇光學急跌逾一成","createTime":"2020-05-18T04:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:54:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3a584e0577b6319fec99a2a512ac4d530dd71c79","tid":2021952,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"日媒指台積電停止接受華為新訂單<br />\n18.05.2020 12:40<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒引述消息人士指，剛宣布在美國設廠的台灣晶片代工企業台積電，已停止接受中國電訊設備製造商華為的新訂單，將履行已下達訂單，向華為供應到9月中旬。台積電未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n美方限制全球使用美國設備的科技及軟件公司，除非獲華府許可，否則不能向華為供貨。國家商務部表示堅決反對，敦促美方立即停止錯誤做法，強調中方將採取必要措施，維護中國企業的合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港股中午升94點舜宇光學急跌逾一成<br />\n18.05.2020 12:34<br />\n<br />\n港股靠穩，恒生指數低開60點後調頭回升逾百點，高見23952點，中午收報23892點，升94點，成交額593億元，國企指數報9709點，升35點。<br />\n<br />\n重磅股騰訊(<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7936f606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>)反覆靠穩，報421.4元，升0.2元，阿里巴巴(<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=200b01b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>)升逾2%，報202元，中移動(<a href=\"http://00941.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00941.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=3819754a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00941.HK</a>)升1%，報57.25元。石油石化股跟隨油價上升，中海油(<a href=\"http://00883.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00883.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=8a116d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00883.HK</a>)升6%，報8.93元，升0.51元，是半日升幅最大藍籌，中石油(<a href=\"http://00857.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00857.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=e8bf62d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00857.HK</a>)升逾4%，報2.67元，是升幅第二大藍籌，中石化(<a href=\"http://00386.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00386.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=905cd03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00386.HK</a>)升近3%，報3.62元。<br />\n<br />\n市場憂慮華為受制裁拖累5G手機出貨量，手機設備股受壓，舜宇光學(<a href=\"http://02382.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02382.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=a819406e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02382.HK</a>)急跌逾一成，報109.5元，跌13元，是半日跌幅最大藍籌，瑞聲科技(<a href=\"http://02018.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02018.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=bf14908f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02018.HK</a>)首季純利大跌近88%，股價跌逾5%，報40.25元，比亞迪電子(<a href=\"http://00285.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00285.HK&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=2bac7d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00285.HK</a>)跌近7%，報16.34元，跌1.22元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288266&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288266%26csid%3D261_341&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCUkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=25e1c17d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288266&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}